            <title><![CDATA[This Beloved Post-Apocalyptic Shooter Is Now Free On PC For A Limited Time]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/this-beloved-post-apocalyptic-shooter-is-now-free-on-pc-for-a-limited-time/1100-6530846/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/this-beloved-post-apocalyptic-shooter-is-now-free-on-pc-for-a-limited-time.1163928/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/this-beloved-post-apocalyptic-shooter-is-now-free-on-pc-for-a-limited-time/1100-6530846/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6530846">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>To celebrate the 15 year anniversary of the Metro first-person shooter franchise, Metro 2033 Redux is available entirely for free on PC for the next 48 hours.</p><p>From today until April 16, players will be able to claim Metro 2033 Redux for free on both <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/286690/Metro_2033_Redux/" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Steam</a> and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=This+Beloved+Post-Apocalyptic+Shooter+Is+Now+Free+On+PC+For+A+Limited+Time&amp;fnauthor=yinyangfooey&amp;fndate=2025-04-14+09%3A09%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2025-04-14+09%3A57%3A53&amp;fnarticle_id=6530846&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Standard+News&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%2Fclick-100770772-15232592%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.gog.com%252Fen%252Fgame%252Fmetro_2033_redux&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fthis-beloved-post-apocalyptic-shooter-is-now-free-on-pc-for-a-limited-time%2F1100-6530846%2F&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">GOG</a>. It's also Steam Deck verified. The game takes place in the year 2033 where the world was devastated by an apocalyptic event 20 years prior. The event destroyed almost all of humankind, subsequently turning Earth's surface into an uninhabitable and poisonous wasteland. A handful of survivors sought shelter in Moscow's underground and civilization entered a new Dark Age.</p><p>Metro 2033 Redux is a rebuilt version of the original game in the 4A Engine. All gameplay improvements and features from Metro: Last Light have been applied to Metro 2033 Redux.</p><p>The entire Metro franchise is having a deep sale on <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/bundle/13326/Metro_Saga_Bundle/" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Steam</a> and GOG as well. Metro Exodus and its expansion pass are getting a 75% and 80% discount, respectively. Individually, the prices for Sam's Story and The Two Colonels DLC for Metro Exodus are 80% and 72% off, respectively. Metro: Last Light Redux is also 85% off. The sale ends on April 21.</p><p>In GameSpot's <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/metro-redux-review/1900-6415843/" data-ref-id="1900-6415843">Metro 2033 review</a>, we called the game, called the game, "an excellent tour through the best and worst of a society in ruins."</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
                                  </div>

          
        
                              
