            <title><![CDATA[Call Of Duty: Warzone Dev Discusses Verdansk's Return And Feedback So Far]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/call-of-duty-warzone-dev-discusses-verdansks-return-and-feedback-so-far/1100-6530838/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
